1
00:00:07,400 --> 00:00:11,460
♪Just To Meet You, you fell for me♪

2
00:00:11,480 --> 00:00:15,460
♪Just to meet me, into my trap you fell♪

3
00:00:15,460 --> 00:00:19,240
♪Wanna try a breathless love?♪

4
00:00:19,240 --> 00:00:23,490
♪Every move hits the heart, close and sure♪

5
00:00:23,490 --> 00:00:27,460
♪Just To Meet You, you love my playful charm♪

6
00:00:27,460 --> 00:00:31,480
♪Just to meet me,
my romantic little schemes for you♪

7
00:00:31,480 --> 00:00:35,170
♪Wanna play another brand-new game?♪

8
00:00:35,170 --> 00:00:40,360
♪Layer by layer, we close the gap♪

9
00:00:40,380 --> 00:00:47,140
=Just To Meet You=

10
00:01:03,380 --> 00:01:05,340
=Episode 3=
=The Holy Maiden Arrives=

11
00:01:12,950 --> 00:01:13,950
Kneel.

12
00:01:15,870 --> 00:01:16,710
Master.

13
00:01:16,950 --> 00:01:19,710
Young Master's return may be a good thing.

14
00:01:20,710 --> 00:01:22,640
(Li Zhongtian, Chairman of the Li Group)
In that case,

15
00:01:22,640 --> 00:01:24,640
all those rumors outside

16
00:01:24,640 --> 00:01:26,480
about brothers turning against each other,

17
00:01:26,480 --> 00:01:28,100
about the Li family splitting up,

18
00:01:28,100 --> 00:01:29,680
(Li Hong, Second Young Master)
will disappear.

19
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:31,350
Now that Young Master is back,

20
00:01:31,350 --> 00:01:32,310
rumors will surely

21
00:01:32,310 --> 00:01:33,150
blow over.

22
00:01:36,230 --> 00:01:37,120
Father.

23
00:01:37,120 --> 00:01:38,870
I've finished the handover

24
00:01:38,870 --> 00:01:40,150
for the hospital we acquired today.

25
00:01:40,560 --> 00:01:41,920
My brother's back at the perfect time.

26
00:01:42,150 --> 00:01:42,990
He can take over management.

27
00:01:43,350 --> 00:01:44,190
With him,

28
00:01:44,430 --> 00:01:46,510
the Li Group will rise again.

29
00:01:48,230 --> 00:01:49,280
Seems like

30
00:01:50,310 --> 00:01:51,950
none of you actually wanted me back.

31
00:01:53,150 --> 00:01:54,070
Master.

32
00:01:54,070 --> 00:01:54,950
Please calm down.

33
00:01:57,760 --> 00:01:59,070
Our Li family

34
00:01:59,070 --> 00:02:00,480
has a century-old legacy,

35
00:02:00,950 --> 00:02:03,000
why must it depend on this unfilial son?

36
00:02:03,120 --> 00:02:04,400
He looks more like

37
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:06,120
he's here to destroy the family.

38
00:02:07,200 --> 00:02:08,190
Young Master,

39
00:02:08,190 --> 00:02:09,240
hurry and apologize to your father.

40
00:02:09,470 --> 00:02:10,310
Hurry.

41
00:02:10,470 --> 00:02:11,360
Just apologize.

42
00:02:16,310 --> 00:02:17,150
Father!

43
00:02:17,520 --> 00:02:19,080
Give my brother whatever he wants.

44
00:02:19,590 --> 00:02:21,030
I admit I'm not as capable as he is.

45
00:02:21,750 --> 00:02:23,280
The future of the Li family

46
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:25,470
should be entrusted to him anyway.

47
00:02:31,310 --> 00:02:32,150
Master.

48
00:02:32,430 --> 00:02:33,310
It just so happens

49
00:02:33,310 --> 00:02:35,710
the master
who picked an auspicious date is here.

50
00:02:37,430 --> 00:02:38,630
Why not have him

51
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:42,960
cleanse Young Master of bad luck?

52
00:02:46,360 --> 00:02:47,240
Welcome

53
00:02:47,240 --> 00:02:48,360
the sorcerer.

54
00:02:48,360 --> 00:02:49,560
Please take the seat of honor.

55
00:02:53,150 --> 00:02:55,800
Kunping, Kunping,

56
00:02:57,430 --> 00:02:59,150
by the command of blood,

57
00:02:59,280 --> 00:03:01,560
with the power of the Baleng blade,

58
00:03:01,560 --> 00:03:03,470
suppress all evil in every direction!

59
00:03:14,310 --> 00:03:15,430
He is cursed with great misfortune.

60
00:03:24,870 --> 00:03:27,870
You're the one Master trusts the most now.

61
00:03:28,030 --> 00:03:30,240
Now it's your turn to perform.

62
00:03:31,080 --> 00:03:33,030
Rest easy, Ma'am.

63
00:03:33,360 --> 00:03:37,680
I've invited a powerful master from our sect.

64
00:03:38,630 --> 00:03:40,150
Even if

65
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:41,910
Young Master survives,

66
00:03:42,470 --> 00:03:44,430
he'll suffer greatly.

67
00:03:45,870 --> 00:03:48,360
Young Master's evil aura

68
00:03:49,400 --> 00:03:51,710
can only be cleared

69
00:03:52,590 --> 00:03:54,400
by the Holy Maiden.

70
00:03:56,800 --> 00:03:57,960
Master,

71
00:03:58,430 --> 00:04:00,630
please invite the Holy Maiden.

72
00:04:02,400 --> 00:04:04,710
Please bring the Holy Maiden here!

73
00:04:40,160 --> 00:04:41,750
Bow in respect before Holy Maiden.

74
00:04:49,680 --> 00:04:51,160
Bow in respect before Holy Maiden.

75
00:04:51,720 --> 00:04:53,270
The Holy Maiden has manifested!

76
00:05:00,950 --> 00:05:03,800
This man is possessed by evil energy.

77
00:05:04,480 --> 00:05:06,270
Holy Maiden,

78
00:05:07,680 --> 00:05:08,680
please dispel it.

79
00:05:26,800 --> 00:05:27,870
Holy Maiden,

80
00:05:28,830 --> 00:05:30,430
please drive out the evil.

81
00:05:37,510 --> 00:05:38,470
Holy Maiden, you...

82
00:05:42,270 --> 00:05:43,630
You're drowning in debt,

83
00:05:43,800 --> 00:05:45,000
your powers are gone,

84
00:05:45,070 --> 00:05:47,720
and you still pretend to be divine?

85
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:50,440
He...

86
00:05:53,950 --> 00:05:54,790
You fraud!

87
00:05:55,190 --> 00:05:56,310
How dare you scam us!

88
00:05:56,920 --> 00:05:57,830
- Guards!
- You...

89
00:05:57,950 --> 00:05:59,600
Throw this fraud out!

90
00:06:01,160 --> 00:06:02,000
Evil spirit,

91
00:06:02,160 --> 00:06:03,750
you dare possess the Madam's body?

92
00:06:04,160 --> 00:06:06,630
Withdraw at once!

93
00:06:08,560 --> 00:06:09,560
You crazy woman!

94
00:06:10,040 --> 00:06:11,360
How dare you hit me!

95
00:06:11,430 --> 00:06:12,430
Such foul language,

96
00:06:12,680 --> 00:06:14,630
it really is an evil spirit at work.

97
00:06:15,040 --> 00:06:15,900
Not good.

98
00:06:15,920 --> 00:06:17,070
The spirit has shifted again!

99
00:06:18,070 --> 00:06:20,630
I see dark haze coiling round you,

100
00:06:21,270 --> 00:06:22,360
let me

101
00:06:22,510 --> 00:06:23,480
send you on your way!

102
00:06:26,630 --> 00:06:27,520
Son.

103
00:06:27,520 --> 00:06:28,630
That's enough!

104
00:06:29,070 --> 00:06:30,480
All of you, get out!

105
00:06:31,120 --> 00:06:32,120
Father, easy.

106
00:06:33,800 --> 00:06:34,640
The Holy Maiden

107
00:06:35,480 --> 00:06:36,560
really is performing an exorcism.

108
00:06:39,310 --> 00:06:40,150
Mother.

109
00:06:41,270 --> 00:06:42,600
How could you be fooled?

110
00:06:43,000 --> 00:06:44,480
Good thing Xue isn't here today.

111
00:06:46,680 --> 00:06:49,160
All you think about is Murong Xue.

112
00:06:49,950 --> 00:06:51,800
You're going to
lose your place in the Li family.

113
00:06:52,120 --> 00:06:53,560
If she finds out about this,

114
00:06:54,270 --> 00:06:55,680
don't you think she'd instantly

115
00:06:56,200 --> 00:06:58,390
run back to her childhood love,

116
00:06:58,510 --> 00:06:59,480
Ye Lang.

117
00:07:00,070 --> 00:07:01,720
(So Ye Lang's childhood sweetheart)

118
00:07:01,720 --> 00:07:03,240
(is his brother's fiancée.)

119
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:05,630
(Classic rich-family drama.)

120
00:07:05,800 --> 00:07:06,680
Young Master.

121
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:09,630
I can tell you possess a pure yang body.

122
00:07:09,920 --> 00:07:11,920
May I borrow it temporarily

123
00:07:12,160 --> 00:07:13,360
to suppress the evil spirit?

124
00:07:13,650 --> 00:07:14,510
I shall comply

125
00:07:14,510 --> 00:07:15,500
with your arrangement.

126
00:07:16,310 --> 00:07:17,150
Stop right there!

127
00:07:17,750 --> 00:07:18,590
You're not the Holy Maiden.

128
00:07:19,070 --> 00:07:19,910
Who exactly are you?

129
00:07:20,120 --> 00:07:21,190
She's a fraud

130
00:07:21,190 --> 00:07:22,070
I hired with money!

131
00:07:22,070 --> 00:07:23,120
Quick.

132
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:24,270
Go get her.

133
00:07:25,600 --> 00:07:26,920
She's indeed not the Holy Maiden.

134
00:07:30,560 --> 00:07:32,830
She's my lawfully wedded wife,

135
00:07:33,480 --> 00:07:34,390
Jiang Niannian.

136
00:07:51,190 --> 00:07:52,030
Ye Lang.

137
00:08:00,920 --> 00:08:02,480
I sold you

138
00:08:02,920 --> 00:08:03,920
and you don't resent me at all?

139
00:08:05,480 --> 00:08:06,320
I don't.

140
00:08:11,480 --> 00:08:12,830
Does someone like you

141
00:08:13,240 --> 00:08:15,160
really exist in this world?

142
00:08:19,430 --> 00:08:21,360
The Holy Maiden can tell fortunes.

143
00:08:21,920 --> 00:08:23,120
Then tell me

144
00:08:24,190 --> 00:08:25,720
why the person I love has come back.

145
00:08:27,560 --> 00:08:29,240
I came back to save you.

146
00:08:30,040 --> 00:08:31,680
As for selling you before,

147
00:08:32,320 --> 00:08:33,510
let's call it even.

148
00:08:34,000 --> 00:08:35,360
Just let it go.

149
00:08:35,360 --> 00:08:36,200
Okay?

150
00:08:38,030 --> 00:08:39,510
Of course we can't call it even.

151
00:08:40,910 --> 00:08:42,320
You dumped me twice.

152
00:08:43,320 --> 00:08:45,120
And you lied to me too, didn't you?

153
00:08:45,120 --> 00:08:46,320
You said you were an orphan.

154
00:08:46,840 --> 00:08:48,080
Turns out you have a stepmother

155
00:08:48,080 --> 00:08:48,960
and a younger brother.

156
00:08:50,510 --> 00:08:51,350
Those people

157
00:08:53,080 --> 00:08:54,390
are not my family at all.

158
00:08:56,080 --> 00:08:57,840
They even wanted me dead.

159
00:08:58,910 --> 00:08:59,910
Wanted you dead?

160
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:02,960
I really have no one left but you.

161
00:09:04,120 --> 00:09:05,960
The only person I care about is you.

162
00:09:07,120 --> 00:09:07,960
Then what about your

163
00:09:08,440 --> 00:09:10,120
childhood sweetheart,

164
00:09:10,670 --> 00:09:11,510
Murong Xue?

165
00:09:11,870 --> 00:09:14,200
She's just someone I knew as a kid.

166
00:09:14,790 --> 00:09:16,630
Stop bringing up someone so irrelevant,

167
00:09:16,630 --> 00:09:17,470
okay?

168
00:09:19,510 --> 00:09:21,360
She's irrelevant.

169
00:09:22,360 --> 00:09:24,270
Then who is important?

170
00:09:32,440 --> 00:09:33,600
You.

171
00:09:36,360 --> 00:09:37,360
(Jiang Niannian,)

172
00:09:37,720 --> 00:09:39,080
(remember why you're here.)

173
00:09:39,790 --> 00:09:41,240
(Use Ye Lang without hesitation)

174
00:09:41,240 --> 00:09:42,200
(to find Jiang Xiaodi.)

175
00:09:43,080 --> 00:09:44,200
Of course.

176
00:09:45,550 --> 00:09:47,120
After all,

177
00:09:47,120 --> 00:09:49,390
I said I'd help you myself

178
00:09:49,390 --> 00:09:51,320
get rid of the evil spirit.

179
00:10:16,000 --> 00:10:17,960
Why are you up so early?

180
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:21,000
Because

181
00:10:21,750 --> 00:10:24,200
I want to be the first to say morning.

182
00:10:35,550 --> 00:10:36,750
I haven't been to the office lately.

183
00:10:37,150 --> 00:10:39,240
Too much work has piled up there.

184
00:10:41,120 --> 00:10:42,030
Then you'd better get going.

185
00:10:44,720 --> 00:10:45,560
Now go.

186
00:10:47,240 --> 00:10:48,200
Alright, I'm going.

187
00:11:05,150 --> 00:11:06,720
What's with Ye Lang?

188
00:11:07,240 --> 00:11:09,120
Why is he living in such a cute room?

189
00:11:20,750 --> 00:11:21,590
Xiaodi!

190
00:11:22,510 --> 00:11:23,350
Xiaodi!

191
00:11:24,150 --> 00:11:24,990
(Xiaodi.)

192
00:11:25,270 --> 00:11:26,870
(Once I've secured my position here,)

193
00:11:27,200 --> 00:11:28,790
(I'll find you very soon.)

194
00:11:31,390 --> 00:11:32,720
(How long is he going to keep this up?)

195
00:11:35,360 --> 00:11:36,720
I don't buy it.

196
00:11:36,720 --> 00:11:39,270
No man falls in love that easily.

197
00:12:00,650 --> 00:12:07,240
♪Stitched-up lips
tear open a blood-red dusk♪

198
00:12:09,050 --> 00:12:15,260
♪You return reborn,
seeing through all my cracks♪

199
00:12:15,810 --> 00:12:22,810
♪This tenderness, a trap or a gift?♪

200
00:12:23,560 --> 00:12:26,030
♪Still, I'd wager my next life on it♪

201
00:12:26,030 --> 00:12:31,030
♪Just for a moment to recognize you again♪

202
00:12:31,030 --> 00:12:35,260
♪You are the blazing light in my despair♪

203
00:12:35,770 --> 00:12:39,700
♪Lighting the edges of my frozen wings♪

204
00:12:39,750 --> 00:12:43,540
♪I burn myself,
leaping into an illusion of fire♪

205
00:12:43,540 --> 00:12:49,290
♪Breaking free
from dead vines in the ashes♪

206
00:12:49,290 --> 00:12:53,610
♪You are the brightest star in the night♪

207
00:12:53,650 --> 00:12:57,470
♪Awakening my dormant fate♪

208
00:12:57,480 --> 00:13:01,970
♪Freeing me from this half-life prison♪

209
00:13:02,000 --> 00:13:06,830
♪As the bells shatter the past♪

210
00:13:07,230 --> 00:13:13,770
♪Life finds its way again♪

